title: Holy Trinity Church, Miejsce Odrzańskie
text:
Holy Trinity Church in <a href="Miejsce%20Odrza%C5%84skie">Miejsce Odrzańskie</a>, Poland, is a <a href="wood">wood</a>en <a href="chapel%20of%20ease">chapel of ease</a> belonging to <a href="Saint%20George">St. George's</a> Parish in <a href="S%C5%82awik%C3%B3w">Sławików</a>, part of the <a href="Roman%20Catholic%20Diocese%20of%20Opole">Roman Catholic Diocese of Opole</a>. 
The church was built in 1770 by carpenter Henryk Henschl.
